OL,3,CBrothers to face retrial next year for
OL,4,Calleged airport assault
OL,6,FITV News Granada Reports journalist
OL,7,FAndrew Fletcher reports from Liverpool
OL,8,FCrown Court
OL,10,FTwo brothers accused of assaulting a
OL,11,Fpolice officer at Manchester Airport
OL,12,Fwill face a retrial.
OL,14,FMohammed Fahir Amaaz, 20, was found
OL,15,Fguilty of assaulting a member of the
OL,16,Fpublic and two female police officers
OL,17,Fduring an incident which later went
OL,18,Fviral on social media.
