OL,3,CBrothers to face retrial next year for
OL,4,Calleged airport assault
OL,6,FThe jury at Liverpool Crown Court, who
OL,7,Fspent 10 hours deliberating, could not
OL,8,Freach a verdict on allegations Amaaz
OL,9,Fand his brother Muhammad Amaad, 26,
OL,10,Fassaulted PC Zachary Marsden causing
OL,11,Factual bodily harm.
OL,13,FAt a hearing on Thursday, Judge Neil
OL,14,FFlewitt KC fixed a retrial for 7 April
OL,15,F2026, with the case estimated to last
OL,16,Fthree to four weeks.
OL,18,FThe court was told professional
OL,19,Fcommitments of defence counsel meant
OL,20,Fthe trial could not be heard before
OL,21,Fthen.
