OL,3,CBrothers to face retrial next year for
OL,4,Calleged airport assault
OL,6,FA bail application for Amaaz, who was
OL,7,Fremanded in custody after the verdicts
OL,8,Fwere returned, was adjourned until 26
OL,9,FAugust.
OL,11,FAmaad, who was given unconditional
OL,12,Fbail, shook his brother's hand before
OL,13,Fleaving the dock.
OL,15,FDuring his trial, the jury heard Amaaz
OL,16,Ffloored PC Lydia Ward with a punch to
OL,17,Fthe face which broke her nose and also
OL,18,Fknocked PC Ellie Cook to the ground.
