OL,3,CBrothers to face retrial next year for
OL,4,Calleged airport assault
OL,6,FBoth officers and PC Marsden
OL,7,Fapproached Amaaz, 20, at a car park
OL,8,Fticket machine after a report that a
OL,9,Fmale fitting his description had
OL,10,Fheadbutted a customer at Starbucks
OL,11,Fcafe in T2 arrivals on 23 July 2024.
OL,13,FAmaaz allegedly resisted and his
OL,14,Fbrother was said to have intervened as
OL,15,Fthe prosecution said they inflicted a
OL,16,F"high level of violence" on the
OL,17,FGreater Manchester Police officers.
