OL,3,CBrothers to face retrial next year for
OL,4,Calleged airport assault
OL,6,FBoth defendants, from Rochdale,
OL,7,FGreater Manchester, told the court
OL,8,Fthey acted in lawful self-defence, or
OL,9,Fin defence of the other.
OL,11,FThe jury found Amaaz guilty of the
OL,12,Fassault of PC Ward causing actual
OL,13,Fbodily harm and the assault of
OL,14,Femergency worker PC Cook.
OL,16,FHe was also convicted of the Starbucks
OL,17,Fassault of a member of the public,
OL,18,FAbdulkareem Ismaeil.
