OL,3,CBrothers to face retrial next year for
OL,4,Calleged airport assault
OL,6,FMobile phone footage of a kick and
OL,7,Fstamp by PC Marsden as Amaaz lay on
OL,8,Fthe floor was shared on social media
OL,9,Fand went viral.
OL,11,FGiving evidence, Amaaz said he feared
OL,12,Fthe "lunatic" male officer would
OL,13,F"batter him to death" and Amaad said
OL,14,Fhe believed he was under attack.
OL,16,FThe defence said the officers used
OL,17,F"unlawful force" as they grabbed Amaaz
OL,18,Ffrom behind without announcing
OL,19,Fthemselves.
